Files: pbgp /usr/local/sbin
Description: PicoBGP - tiny routing advertising daemon
  picobgp is minimalistic daemon for subnetworks advertising and route topology update.
  .
  The picobgp daemon is written in C and is really simple to use. 
  It support a small list of option and allow you to advertise a given subnet on an interface of your pc.
  The subnet announce is sent using broadcast address on the device link and all the hosts on the same connection can be felt by the announce.
